      <p>The reason some people doubt whether whitening strips work is that not all teeth whitening strips are created equal. Cheap, poorly made strips slip around, deliver an uneven dose of gel, and often cause sensitivity. That is exactly why we engineered the 3DWhiteningStrips formula differently. Our whitening strips use an advanced no-slip grip that keeps the gel in contact with every tooth, an enamel-safe concentration that minimizes sensitivity, and a precise, even coating that produces consistent results. In our own testing, the enamel-safe formula lifted visible stains after a single 7-day treatment — proof that the right whitening strips really do work.</p>

