      <h3>Recommended Whitening Strips for Sensitive Teeth</h3>
      <p>If you have sensitive teeth, you may have avoided whitening strips in the past, worried about discomfort. We designed our teeth whitening strips specifically with sensitivity in mind. The 3DWhiteningStrips formula uses a carefully balanced peroxide concentration and protective compounds that whiten effectively while keeping sensitivity to a minimum, so you can whiten comfortably even with sensitive teeth. That is why we designed these as the recommended whitening strips for anyone who wants a whiter smile without the sting.</p>

