      <h3>How to Use Your 3DWhiteningStrips Teeth Whitening Strips</h3>
      <p>Getting the most out of your whitening strips is simple. Peel a strip from its backing and press it gently onto your upper teeth, then repeat with a strip for your lower teeth. Smooth the strips down so the gel makes full contact with the enamel. Leave your teeth whitening strips in place for 30 minutes while you go about your day, then peel them off and rinse. For the best results, use your whitening strips once a day for the full 7-day treatment, and avoid eating or drinking for 30 minutes afterward. Most people notice a difference within three to five days, with optimal results after a full week — a routine that makes 3DWhiteningStrips the easiest and best whitening strips to fit into a busy life.</p>

